    • renderTypes

      public SimpleBakedModel.Builder renderTypes(RenderTypeGroup renderTypes)
      Sets the render type to be used for this model, and will be used for any graphics setting.

      If you need to set a specific render type for fast graphics, consider using renderTypes(RenderTypeGroup, RenderTypeGroup) instead which allows choosing render types for both fancy and fast graphics.

      另请参阅:
      • renderTypes(RenderTypeGroup, RenderTypeGroup)
      API Note:
      If this model is for leaves and if the given render type is either cutout or cutout mipped, it will be overridden with solid when fast graphics is enabled.
